  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Heroes Arena!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n===<br />\r\nFEATURES<br />\r\n===<br />\r\n1. Endless Arena <br />\r\n2. Loot Corridor<br />\r\n3. Variety of monsters to defeat<br />\r\n4. Max Player level of 200.<br />\r\n5. Player skins<br />\r\n6. Weapon Shop<br />\r\n7. Potion Shop<br />\r\n8. General Shop<br />\r\n9. A small secret area<br />\r\n10. Steam Achievements<br />\r\n<br />\r\n===<br />\r\nHOW TO PLAY<br />\r\n===<br />\r\n1. Use ( W, S, D, A ) to move the player<br />\r\n2. 'Left Mouse Button' to attack<br />\r\n3. 'Right Mouse Button' to use skill \"Big Sword\"\"<br />\r\n4. 'Space' to use skill \"Spin Attack\"<br />\r\n5. '1' to use HP Potion",
